Topic	Details
âœ… What is DevOps?	CI/CD, Infrastructure as Code, Agile methodology
âœ… Azure DevOps Overview	Services: Repos, Pipelines, Boards, Artifacts, Test Plans
âœ… Project Structure	Organization â†’ Project â†’ Repo/Pipeline/Board/etc.

ðŸ§© Phase 2: Set Up Azure DevOps Account
